snippet.title: Fake Gun Disarming Videos on the Internet and What you REALLY Need To Know | Ryan Hoover
snippet.description:

Ryan Hoover talking about gun disarms and you don't need a bunch of new techniques.

Follow the Entire Aperture Team!

All of our videos are for educational and entertainment purposes only.  Please do not try any of the actions you see in our videos.  Train under the qualified guidance of an instructor.  Consult your physician.  Listen to your body.  Understand your limitations and capabilities.  Have fun.  Hope to see you in one of our seminars!

Get notified of training events in your area: http://bit.ly/2t5KdHZ
